desc: Chef Stacey Dougan is a master vegan chef and restaurateur. She owns Simply Pure and is set to launch her next venture.

layout.text: Chef Stacey is a master vegan chef with over 10 years of culinary experience. Her impressive culinary background includes training with James Beard Award winning chefs. She globally revered as vegan chef who continues to create recipes that are both nutritious and infused.
